summary: Character made from a variety of mods
descriptionHtml:
A save file made up of many different character mods

Looks extremely awesome to me at least

Mods Required (install in this order):

For Body and Skin:
1. UNP BASE Skinny Body V1dot2
http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/6709

2. UNPB 2p2 Blessed Body (no BBP)
http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/14899

For Hair:
3. MTOH v 2_5 (My Type Of Hair):
http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/6173

For Head:
4: http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/7127 (doesn\'t matter too much, does not effect looks)

For Face: (choose your own style CBBE or UNP etc.)
http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/7897

This save file and character is made by me, however the mods ARE NOT made by me.

I have no say of what you can do with the Files
